value.name: Hyatt Regency Auckland • New Zealand
value.snippet: Hyatt Regency Auckland Hotel Offering a wellness centre and a spa area, the luxury Hyatt Regency Auckland Hotel is located near Highwic History Museum. The venue is 0.5 km away from the state-integrated secondary school "Saint Peter's College" and 2.2 km from Spark Arena. The city centre is about 10 minutes away on foot.

value.name: Boutique 5 Star Hotel on the Water's Edge | Park Hyatt Auckland
value.snippet: Park Hyatt Auckland is perfectly located on the water’s edge and will offer expansive views across Wynyard Quarter's Lighter Basin and out to the Waitematā Harbour. Our sophisticated waterfront residence has 195 guestrooms, four restaurants and bars, versatile and elegant event spaces, a day spa, a 25-metre infinity pool, and a full fitness center.

value.name: HYATT REGENCY AUCKLAND HOTEL | GREAT PRICES, BOOK AND SAVE
value.snippet: Hyatt Regency Auckland Hotel Offering a bar and an indoor pool, Hyatt Regency Auckland Hotel is located 1.9 km away from Aotea Public Square. The venue is situated 1 km from Auckland city centre and 20 km from Auckland airport. Waitemata Harbour is less than 0.5 km away.
